comments: Cousins (GSW) makes contact with the ball before it reaches its apex during the jump ball.
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with Leonard's (TOR) arm at the start of his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Green (GSW) moves along Leonard's (TOR) path and absorbs the contact while defending the shot attempt.
Green (TOR) makes marginal contact with Cook (GSW) at the start of his drive, but he is able to move through the contact and stay on his path.
Leonard (TOR) and Cousins (GSW) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Cousins (GSW) has a marginal left hand to Leonard's (TOR) side as he cleanly dislodges the ball at the end of the drive.
Gasol (TOR) and Curry (GSW) briefly engage and separate off-ball.
Green (TOR) makes clean contact with the ball while defending Green's (GSW) drive.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: After communicating with the Replay Center, the call on the floor is overturned to Raptors' ball.
Iguodala (GSW) and Gasol (TOR) briefly engage and separate after the screen.
Leonard (TOR) does not move through Green (GSW) at the start of the drive. Green is already falling backwards when contact occurs.
[Observable in enhanced video] Siakam (TOR) lifts his pivot foot after gathering the pass.
Cousins (GSW) briefly grasps Gasol's (TOR) jersey during the rebound, but does not affect his ability to get to the loose ball.
Green (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position on Leonard (TOR) during the drive.
[Observable in enhanced video] Leonard (TOR) lifts his pivot foot prior to releasing the ball on his dribble.
Cousins (GSW) briefly grasps Gasol's (TOR) jersey during the rebound, but does not affect his team's ability to get the loose ball.
Livingston (GSW) briefly grasps and quickly releases Siakam's (TOR) jersey without affecting his ability to rebound during the loose ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Curry (GSW) lifts his pivot foot after receiving the pass.
VanVleet (TOR) makes marginal contact with Curry's (GSW) arm and does not affect his ability to pass.
Green (TOR) sets the screen on Green (GSW) and does not deliver contact.
Curry (GSW) legally contests Green's (TOR) jump shot attempt and makes incidental "high-five" contact after his release.
